    "multicolumn_review_BdtPMU": {
      "type": "multicolumn-review",
      "blocks": {
        "column_hHiGqY": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "background_color": "#f2f2f2",
            "heading_color": "#000000",
            "text_color": "#333333",
            "title": "Best sleep aid ever!",
            "star_count": 5,
            "star_color": "#f59e0b",
            "title_size": "h3",
            "text": "<p><em>I have had issues staying asleep for months, I tried the Tro Zzz and man what a difference!  Able to drift off to sleep and stay asleep!</em></p><h6>James P, 7/26/2025</h6>",
            "show_popup": false,
            "popup_image_position": "top",
            "justify_text": true,
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "button_style_secondary": false,
            "enable_highlight": false,
            "highlight_style": "marker"
          }
        },
        "column_d6JaRx": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "background_color": "#f2f2f2",
            "heading_color": "#000000",
            "text_color": "#333333",
            "title": "Seems to be helping my sleep, using 1/4 of the square.",
            "star_count": 5,
            "star_color": "#f59e0b",
            "title_size": "h3",
            "text": "<p><em>I'm 63, male, have been having trouble staying asleep for a while now.  Started taking this Tro Zzz at bedtime, seems to help me get into sleep and I seem to be able to fall back asleep after I wake up at 2 or 3am, which I have been doing for years now, but now seem to get back to sleep and stay asleep to 6am.  I also feel more rested.</em><br/></p><h6>Rody Whitfield, 7/01/2025</h6>",
            "show_popup": false,
            "popup_image_position": "top",
            "justify_text": false,
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "button_style_secondary": false,
            "enable_highlight": false,
            "highlight_style": "marker"
          }
        },
        "column_DtUTP9": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "background_color": "#f2f2f2",
            "heading_color": "#000000",
            "text_color": "#333333",
            "title": "Don't know what I'd do without them!",
            "star_count": 5,
            "star_color": "#f59e0b",
            "title_size": "h3",
            "text": "<p><em>I've had an especially difficult menopause, and one of the worst symptoms has been the inability to get more than a few hours sleep per night. I dealt with this for over 8 years before finding a good doctor who provides HRT, and stumbling across Troscriptions. I don't need a dose every night, but I always keep one quarter of a troch on my nightstand. Whenever I wake up and can't get back to sleep, I pop one in my mouth and am shortly snoozing again. It gives me many, many nights' sleep so I can have many more days of being productive instead of dragging. My entire family thanks you!</em></p><h6>Christy, 6/12/2025</h6>",
            "show_popup": false,
            "popup_image_position": "top",
            "justify_text": false,
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "button_style_secondary": false,
            "enable_highlight": false,
            "highlight_style": "marker"
          }
        }
      },
